summary: Completed comprehensive testing of AdOperator app backend APIs and frontend UI. Backend tests fully passed (14/14). Frontend UI mostly functional with minor navigation/auth session issues.

ui_bugs.issue: Session seems to expire during testing, causing redirect to login

integration_issues.issue: Some test runs show login redirect when navigating between pages

passed_tests: All backend CRUD operations (create, read, update, delete analyses)
NEW improve endpoint works correctly (rejects incomplete analyses)
Compliance checker API works (detects risky terms, returns scores)
Analysis form loads with Quick/Complete tabs - both clickable
'Gerar exemplo' button works - fills form with sample data
Compliance banner shows for risky terms (cura, 100%, elimina)
CTA button says 'Encontrar o melhor anuncio'
Dashboard loads and shows analysis list
Form validation prevents submission with empty required fields
success_percentage: Backend: 100% (14/14 tests passed), Frontend: ~85% (most features working, minor session/navigation issues)
